race.comment: CLIFTON LUCA (1) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 1.75 lengths third behind Paid My Dues in 30.27. Has the ability and can measure up.    WEST ON TAPPER (6) makes debut for the Christopher Halse kennel. Profiles well so watch market closely. Something for the Multiples: ASTON NEGRONI (7) AGASSI (4)
